&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;At Two Six Technologies, we build, deploy, and implement innovative products that solve the world’s most complex challenges today. Through unrivaled collaboration and unwavering trust, we push the boundaries of what’s possible to empower our team and support our customers in building a safer global future.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Overview of Opportunity&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Two Six Technologies is actively seeking an Automation Tester to support motivated to learn and contribute to a growing team that is solving complex problems for our intelligence community. &amp;nbsp;We work in a fast-paced, collaborative, inclusive, and iterative delivery environment. This role will be primarily responsible for developing and maintaining automated end-to-end, integration and performance tests.&amp;nbsp; This position offers the opportunity to provide robust and comprehensive testing of features that serve an enterprise level tool supporting users across the IC and the DoW.&lt;/p&gt;
