&lt;li&gt;Performs manual testing as stop-gap for automated testing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develops functional, end-to-end, regression, and performance tests in automated test environments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Detects and writes software bug reports and feature requests&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understands, reproduces, troubleshoots product defects and works with developers to determine the best resolution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assists in the planning and implementation of testing new features&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you will need:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
