&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of test design patterns and best practices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Git version control and collaborative workflows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understanding of software development lifecycle and agile methodologies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical and debugging skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent written communication for test documentation and defect reporting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working collaboratively with development teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to haves:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong programming skills in JavaScript/TypeScript&lt;/li&gt;
