&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reverse Engineering Tooling:&lt;/strong&gt; Practical experience performing light architectural reverse engineering or control-flow analysis on firmware images using tools such as Ghidra, IDA Pro, or Binary Ninja.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Emulation &amp;amp; Rehosting:&lt;/strong&gt; Hands-on experience configuring or modifying embedded binaries to support successful firmware rehosting within emulation frameworks like QEMU.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Security Clearance:&lt;/strong&gt; An active Top Secret security clearance, with the verified capability to obtain and maintain a TS/SCI clearance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location:&lt;/strong&gt; Ability to work in the Two Six office in Herndon, Virginia daily.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to have (preferred):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
